# [% .ProjectName %]

[% .Description %]
[%- if .HasCLI %]

## Commands

```bash
[% .BinaryName %] --help              # Show available commands
[% .BinaryName %] version             # Show version info
[% .BinaryName %] v                   # Alias for version
[% .BinaryName %] completion bash     # Shell completion: bash|zsh|fish|powershell
[%- if .Config %]
[% .BinaryName %] --config ./config.yaml config path
[% .BinaryName %] config init         # Create user config
[% .BinaryName %] config get <key>    # Read a config value
[% .BinaryName %] config set <key> <value>
[% .BinaryName %] config toggle <key> # Toggle a boolean value
[% .BinaryName %] config keys         # List configurable keys
[%- end %]
```
[%- end %]
[%- if .HasLib %]

## Library Usage

