import "[% .ModulePath %]/pkg/[% .LibPackage %]"
```
[%- end %]

## Project Structure

Includes: Makefile, CI pipelines, assets/ directory, .gitignore, LICENSE[%- if .Community %], SECURITY.md[%- end %][%- if .Changelog %], CHANGELOG.yaml + CHANGELOG.md[%- end %][%- if .Todo %], TODO.md[%- end %].
